# Assets Loans And Advances Including Tainted Amount

## identifier
de7623

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of loans and advances receivable by the reporting party as at the relevant date, including tainted held-to-maturity investments. This item is to be determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndAdvancesIncludingTainted.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
